    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "The Laboratory Management Department is fully committed to maintaining high standards of quality, overall safety, and compliance within the laboratory while ensuring smooth and efficient operation. We implement complementary management regulations and safety policies to protect the safety of the students, faculty, staff, and the university community and provide various experimental equipment and instruments. Our efforts provide students with hands-on experience with course concepts and the opportunity to explore different experimental methods, ensure the well-being of laboratory personnel, and meet regulatory requirements."
